divs: Sighting DetailsIt was not a plane. Plane or Heli. travels in straight. But this was not like that. It had three to four corners with White light that was flickering on all sides of the object. The object was going in a wave like motion. I mean it was going in one direction, with a Sine wave pattern. (Slowly up and slowly down). It was going from South to North Direction. I saw it over some where on the east of I405.
